{"tid":1484013,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢一刻，我想喊，多謝咁多位香港人，Proud of you","createTime":"2019-08-18T13:55:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T13:08:09.000Z","uid":52090,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7c2a4ead0bf7469d52fe28db1a392c05c7ee7815","tid":1484013,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:55:24.000Z","msg":"呢一刻，我想喊，<br />\n<br />\n好老實講，最近兩星期，我開始攰，<br />\n<br />\n開始係到諗，我每日mon post，<br />\n每日起底，識破三毛分化撚，係唔係有用<br />\n<br />\n開始係到諗，每星期企出黎，<br />\n零消費，零享樂，係唔係值得<br />\n<br />\n開始係到諗，用左無數時間，<br />\n兩個月開左廿幾個Post，係唔係有用<br />\n<br />\n但今日，係你地話我知，持續左兩個月，<br />\n香港人仲未灰心，香港人團火仲係到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地一日肯企出黎，<br />\n我一日都會為香港用盡全力，<br />\n我一日都會為香港付出</span></span><br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位香港人！<br />\nProud of you <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"287e030331dbd854d1b6b7be47a2e530ea55780f","tid":1484013,"uid":263177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:58:02.000Z","msg":"支持你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d40627ec47cf08a0356698001d47e55ba86405f8","tid":1484013,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T13:58:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港大家有份，使咩多謝</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f5c6bb7ba6c8f555cf7ecc878e3476fc2851991","tid":1484013,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:03:45.000Z","msg":"69之前，<br />\n發生伊朗油船打算黎香港，<br />\n林奠班子死撐，冇問題，<br />\n香港內政不容美國干涉<br />\n<br />\n果星期，我轉左6位數去其他國家<br />\n<br />\n69當日，一車車白衫去到維園，<br />\n係你地話我知，<br />\n雨傘，魚蛋，唔係民主終結<br />\n香港仲有希望，仲有曙光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DhuAiA0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDhuAiA0.png&h=ee3f9657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34e7800c5277b8c8559d566c2c99276dcb567065","tid":1484013,"uid":269256,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"香港人加油💪"},{"pid":"f5d00e42bb808ce1fdaf4d3d9b711837e7515d96","tid":1484013,"uid":308732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"香港人，係一個會令我自豪既身份。"},{"pid":"220028a25ad1665a99596bca5ada8d8eeaaf08a7","tid":1484013,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:11:16.000Z","msg":"69 當晚，我心情好複雜，<br />\n一方面，為香港103萬人上街而自豪，<br />\n令一方面，為林奠無恥恢復二讀三讀通過而憤怒<br />\n<br />\n同時，勇武派為運動，<br />\n流下第一滴血而擔心，<br />\n同時擔心和理非會割蓆<br />\n<br />\n好好采，和理非經過後雨傘運動，<br />\n明白到，勇武嘅重要性，並無割蓆<br />\n為勇武派打下強心針，<br />\n為日後抗爭打下基礎<br />\n<br />\n好多謝當日公民黨嘅聲名，<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力，<br />\n不割蓆，不分化<br />\n成為呢次革命嘅信念<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">多謝各位勇武，<br />\n多謝各位和理非</span>"},{"pid":"17a62f4d28c3d44d548f15ba9a1f778df8b75259","tid":1484013,"uid":241349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:12:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">WE ARE ONE</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人  一條心<br />\n不割蓆  才會贏</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oZAYG7Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoZAYG7Q.jpg&h=bbad84f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVXL6zq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVXL6zq.jpg&h=dab9e2c8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vrhder.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vrhder.jpg&h=48c4326f&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oc2L6zs.jpg\" d